<tr><td align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="black">

<font face="arial" Size="-1" color="caffb0"><b>In Lesser fay, near the steam font zone, there is a gnome which has no faction hits, only 1000 hp, and gives exp all the way up to level 48.

Her name is Happ Dempledrod (hense happy camp).

The only trick is breaking her spawn, because when you first engage her, the pet will be up.

Root fear or ignore the pet and bring her down fast and hard.

When she spawns again, engage her before she summons a pet.

If you get in trouble, the steamfont zone is RIGHT THERE :)
</b><br></font>
